defaultThe duty will not apply to the project licensing decisions of the Animals in Science Regulation Unit
default.  The industry concerned has specifically asked that project licensing decisions be omitted to avoid harm to the industry, as such decisions assess the level of detriment to animal welfare against the potential benefits of a project. 
default 
defaultThe duty will not apply to the economic regulatory functions of the Civil Aviation Authority
default.
default Including Trinity House Lighthouse Service, the Northern Lighthouse Board and the Commissioner of Irish Lights (in respect of its regulatory functions in 
defaultNorthern Ireland
default)
default The Serious Organised Crime Agency (SOCA) was included in the original consultation on the growth duty. However we have since clarified that they are a police function and it would not therefore be appropriate to bring SOCA within scope of the growth duty for regulatory functions.
